.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-6::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, black, brown, light-blue
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, indie, reggae, rock
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, biathlon, golf, rowing
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person who likes white##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is the fan of rock##1
3. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
4. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
5. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
6. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
7. the person who likes black is on the right of the fan of funk##1
8. the person who likes black is on the left of the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3       |      4       |
| Color           | white    | black   | brown | light-blue |
| Music-Genre   | funk     | reggae   | rock         | indie        |
| Sport         | biathlon | baseball | golf         | rowing       |

