.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-8::.
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, pineapple, watermelon, zucchini
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, orchid, sunflower, balloon-flower
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, mystery, spy, western
1. the person who growsorchid is on the left or right of the person eating pineapple##3
2. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
3. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3
4. the person watching spy movies is on the far right##1
5. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
6. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
7. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3
8. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the person who growsballoon-flower##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |      4      |
| Food          | watermelon | pineapple    | zucchini | broccoli    |
| Flower         | sunflower     | balloon-flower | orchid  | zinnia |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery    | western      | action   | spy         |

