.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, iced-tea, milk
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, gospel, electronic, r&b
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, scooter, snowmobile, train
1. the person drinking almond-milk is the person driving the car##1
2. the fan of d&b is between the person drinking coffee and the fan of r&b##2
3. the fan of gospel is the person driving the train##1
4. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
5. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
6. the person drinking coffee is the fan of electronic##1
7. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
8. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
9. the person driving the snowmobile is the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | coffee      | almond-milk | milk       | iced-tea  |
| Music-Genre       | electronic | d&b | r&b    | gospel |
| Transport   | scooter     | car         | snowmobile | train     |

