4. the owner of the turtle is between the person eating radish and the polish##2
5. the person eating radish is the argentine##1
6. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the argentine##3
7. the owner of the rat is on the far left##1
8. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the person eating raspberry##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |      3       |     4      |
