.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate, lemonade, sprite
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, kale, kiwi, mango
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, january, july, october
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the person eating kiwi is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
6. the person eating mango is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who's birthday is in july##1
8. the person eating asparagus is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking almond-milk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | sprite    | almond-milk | lemonade  |
| Food          | kale          | asparagus | mango       | kiwi      |
| Birthday   | july     | january    | october     | december |

